WEBVTT

01:27.400 --> 01:31.880
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.120 --> 01:34.910
[Episode 17]

02:25.240 --> 02:26.640
Why are you sitting here?

02:27.560 --> 02:28.360
What's wrong?

02:30.079 --> 02:31.410
Are you feeling unwell?

02:35.870 --> 02:37.470
I thought about it all night.

02:37.870 --> 02:38.840
You are right.

02:40.030 --> 02:41.280
We are the same.

02:42.680 --> 02:44.480
I had actually thought about...

02:45.240 --> 02:47.630
completely forgetting Ding Zhibo
for the rest of my life,

02:47.630 --> 02:49.290
not telling anyone about him,

02:49.680 --> 02:50.680
not even you.

02:52.840 --> 02:54.030
Both of us

02:55.870 --> 02:56.630
carry lifelong wounds and shame

02:56.630 --> 02:58.910
that we don't want others to know about.

03:00.030 --> 03:00.710
So...

03:01.470 --> 03:02.240
I'm sorry.

03:05.360 --> 03:07.160
I have no right to criticize you.

03:20.560 --> 03:22.000
You don't have to force yourself

03:22.000 --> 03:23.260
to accept me like this.

03:24.030 --> 03:24.520
Really.

03:25.600 --> 03:26.600
You don't have to.

03:26.760 --> 03:27.820
But I'm willing to.

03:27.870 --> 03:29.079
I'm willing to accept you.

03:29.079 --> 03:30.120
I am.

03:30.520 --> 03:32.650
Just like you accepted me completely.

03:38.280 --> 03:39.750
We both have wounds.

03:41.870 --> 03:43.240
Healing together

03:44.400 --> 03:46.460
is always faster than doing it alone.

03:48.560 --> 03:49.430
I love you.

03:51.680 --> 03:54.680
Your protection and support
are very important to me.

04:02.680 --> 04:03.540
You said before

04:04.080 --> 04:05.150
that no matter how many hardships

04:05.150 --> 04:06.840
you went through
or how misunderstood you were,

04:06.840 --> 04:08.150
you never wanted to give up.

04:08.150 --> 04:10.870
Me too. I don't want to give up either.

04:11.240 --> 04:12.750
I've been struggling to move forward,

04:12.750 --> 04:14.120
and that's how I met you.

04:17.870 --> 04:19.200
There's one more thing.

04:20.360 --> 04:21.160
I lied to you.

04:26.680 --> 04:28.940
When I gave you the marriage certificate

04:29.350 --> 04:31.690
and said I could accept you leaving me,

04:33.960 --> 04:35.050
I was lying.

04:37.040 --> 04:39.100
I was really afraid you would say yes.

04:40.420 --> 04:41.560
I was really afraid

04:41.560 --> 04:42.480
you would actually leave me.

04:42.480 --> 04:43.750
No, I wouldn't.

04:44.510 --> 04:45.240
I wouldn't.

04:45.240 --> 04:47.500
I really can't imagine life without you.

04:49.040 --> 04:49.890
You said

04:51.270 --> 04:52.190
we are

04:53.630 --> 04:55.960
the best gifts
heaven has given each of us.

04:56.360 --> 04:57.750
I won't leave you.

04:58.720 --> 04:59.540
Thank you.

05:00.890 --> 05:02.690
Thank you for not giving up on me.

05:03.480 --> 05:06.080
Thank you for still being willing
to be my wife.

05:06.510 --> 05:07.470
I am willing.

05:07.630 --> 05:08.630
Of course I am.

05:11.560 --> 05:12.960
I can't live without you.

05:13.120 --> 05:13.720
Thank you.

05:14.190 --> 05:15.820
I can't live without you.

05:17.360 --> 05:18.120
I love you.

05:19.190 --> 05:20.840
We must be together forever.

05:20.980 --> 05:22.600
-We can't be apart.
-We will.

05:23.600 --> 05:24.930
I won't let you leave me.

05:26.260 --> 05:26.990
I love you.

05:27.190 --> 05:28.690
I won't leave you.

05:29.360 --> 05:29.960
I love you.

05:30.190 --> 05:31.090
I love you too.

05:36.460 --> 05:37.100
Yuan!

05:37.640 --> 05:38.520
Yuan!

05:39.070 --> 05:39.870
Yuan!

05:40.390 --> 05:41.240
What's wrong?

05:41.680 --> 05:42.480
What's wrong?

05:48.500 --> 05:49.150
Yuan!

05:49.540 --> 05:50.060
Yuan!

05:50.330 --> 05:50.890
Yuan!

05:54.240 --> 05:54.800
Yuan!

05:55.240 --> 05:55.830
Yuan!

05:56.870 --> 05:57.770
Yuan!

05:57.800 --> 05:58.670
Yuan!

06:10.040 --> 06:10.920
You're awake?

06:12.040 --> 06:13.500
Does the wound still hurt?

06:16.230 --> 06:17.370
Do you need my help?

06:17.750 --> 06:19.270
No, I can handle it.

06:20.750 --> 06:22.550
The doctor said you need to rest.

06:24.630 --> 06:26.090
If I let you do everything,

06:26.680 --> 06:27.870
won't my recovery

06:27.870 --> 06:29.160
take longer?

06:30.000 --> 06:31.800
My cooking isn't that bad, is it?

06:32.870 --> 06:34.270
I kind of hope it is.

06:34.680 --> 06:36.750
That way,
I can keep getting an upset stomach

06:36.750 --> 06:38.280
and won't have to go to work.

06:41.560 --> 06:42.430
Let me see.

06:44.270 --> 06:46.530
You look like you've been knocked silly.

06:53.680 --> 06:55.340
I want to go back and visit Mom.

06:57.830 --> 06:58.890
You miss her again?

06:59.560 --> 07:00.120
No.

07:01.800 --> 07:03.330
I'm talking about your mom.

07:04.040 --> 07:05.070
Your real mom.

07:06.480 --> 07:08.680
I want to take Jiale to see her.

07:15.190 --> 07:17.920
Your mom must be very lonely
back home by herself.

07:18.270 --> 07:19.540
If she is willing,

07:19.630 --> 07:20.920
she can move in with us.

07:21.920 --> 07:23.180
Do you really think so?

07:27.360 --> 07:28.360
My mom is gone.

07:29.920 --> 07:31.030
I really regret it.

07:32.520 --> 07:34.800
I missed out on a lot of time with her.

07:36.190 --> 07:38.390
I don't want you to have the same regret.

07:38.750 --> 07:41.040
Don't worry, I will treat your mom

07:41.480 --> 07:43.640
just like my own.

07:45.480 --> 07:46.270
Thank you.

07:47.390 --> 07:50.250
If my mom heard what you just said,

07:51.070 --> 07:52.530
she would be very touched.

07:53.310 --> 07:54.720
If she sees Jiale,

07:55.270 --> 07:57.130
she'll probably be even happier.

08:05.480 --> 08:06.540
It's the hospital.

08:09.070 --> 08:11.530
I still have a bunch of things
waiting for me.

08:15.240 --> 08:15.800
Honey.

08:16.390 --> 08:18.050
When this busy period is over,

08:18.270 --> 08:19.680
you, me, and Jiale—

08:20.830 --> 08:23.630
let's go back to my hometown together
to see my mom.

08:24.240 --> 08:24.720
Okay.

08:39.669 --> 08:40.240
Hello?

08:41.669 --> 08:42.470
What's wrong?

08:42.659 --> 08:43.980
Well... Yuan...

08:44.150 --> 08:47.200
seems to be getting sicker these days.

08:47.480 --> 08:49.610
Sometimes she has epileptic seizures

08:49.720 --> 08:51.480
that won't stop for a long time.

08:51.910 --> 08:54.820
Those medicines don't seem to work either.

08:56.390 --> 09:00.450
Every time she takes them, she complains
of a headache and wants to vomit.

09:00.960 --> 09:03.610
Should we send her to the hospital again?

09:03.720 --> 09:05.440
Are you the doctor, or am I?

09:06.000 --> 09:08.110
It takes time for the medicine to work.

09:08.110 --> 09:09.640
Just feed her as I said.

09:10.080 --> 09:10.790
Don't miss a single day,

09:10.790 --> 09:13.120
and don't miss a single pill, understand?

09:13.870 --> 09:14.510
Got it.

09:21.120 --> 09:23.180
I didn't have time to tell you before.

09:24.480 --> 09:25.280
I got married.

09:27.390 --> 09:28.120
Married?

09:30.030 --> 09:31.000
Who is your wife?

09:31.910 --> 09:33.310
She is a college teacher.

09:34.390 --> 09:35.390
She's a good girl.

09:36.360 --> 09:37.390
I'll find some time later

09:37.390 --> 09:38.650
to bring her to see you.

09:40.840 --> 09:42.720
Okay, sounds good.

09:43.910 --> 09:45.170
Take care of my sister.

09:46.380 --> 09:47.510
Don't make me worry.

10:09.290 --> 10:11.550
[Li Changning]

10:13.870 --> 10:15.050
[Bachelor's Degree Certificate,
Lihai University of Science & Technology]

10:17.960 --> 10:19.630
Ms. Yan, I graduated.

10:19.630 --> 10:20.480
If it weren't for you,

10:20.480 --> 10:21.960
I definitely couldn't have done it.

10:21.960 --> 10:23.150
Thank you so much.

10:23.270 --> 10:25.840
It's a pity you didn't come
to the graduation ceremony.

10:25.840 --> 10:26.870
I miss you so much.

10:29.120 --> 10:30.520
Li Changning graduated?

10:31.670 --> 10:32.530
She's amazing.

10:33.120 --> 10:34.520
Why didn't you go see her?

10:37.270 --> 10:39.130
The school didn't ask me to attend

10:39.750 --> 10:41.550
the graduation ceremony at all.

10:45.870 --> 10:46.600
Makes sense.

10:48.200 --> 10:50.000
From the school's perspective,

10:50.320 --> 10:51.450
I can understand it.

10:54.910 --> 10:56.970
You also think I shouldn't have gone.

10:58.960 --> 11:00.200
You can't expect everyone

11:00.200 --> 11:01.510
to know you like I do.

11:02.390 --> 11:03.790
Right now, to the school,

11:04.670 --> 11:07.440
you're indeed like a hot potato.

11:11.480 --> 11:12.790
Maybe it

11:12.790 --> 11:13.920
sounds harsh to you,

11:15.960 --> 11:17.240
but if it were you,

11:18.510 --> 11:19.510
what would you do?

11:20.910 --> 11:21.510
After all,

11:24.550 --> 11:25.320
that person

11:26.320 --> 11:27.960
made all the letters public.

11:29.510 --> 11:31.840
I know what you went through emotionally.

11:31.870 --> 11:32.670
I also know

11:32.670 --> 11:34.200
how you gradually

11:34.200 --> 11:35.440
fell into his trap.

11:36.390 --> 11:37.990
But the school doesn't know.

11:38.050 --> 11:39.330
Others don't know.

11:39.870 --> 11:41.270
In the eyes of outsiders,

11:41.320 --> 11:44.390
you're just a homewrecker who pursued
someone else's husband

11:44.390 --> 11:45.200
and a liar.

11:53.080 --> 11:54.280
With your abilities,

11:55.080 --> 11:57.280
you can totally take a break for a while.

11:59.270 --> 12:01.670
It will also let
the public outcry die down.

12:02.120 --> 12:04.870
Change your environment and start afresh.

12:08.550 --> 12:09.670
Are you saying

12:10.670 --> 12:11.790
I should resign?

12:18.720 --> 12:19.450
Why should I?

12:20.390 --> 12:22.590
I'm not the one who committed the crime.

12:25.790 --> 12:27.200
Throwing a childish temper tantrum at me

12:27.200 --> 12:28.400
won't do you any good.

12:29.750 --> 12:31.080
Objectively speaking,

12:31.390 --> 12:33.380
you didn't get your professional title,

12:33.380 --> 12:35.720
so even without all this mess,

12:36.000 --> 12:37.870
you might not have been able to stay.

12:37.870 --> 12:39.150
Whether you leave now or not is simply

12:39.150 --> 12:42.210
a matter of who takes the initiative
—the school or you.

12:43.150 --> 12:44.810
Should I just surrender then?

12:47.550 --> 12:49.000
Alright, alright.

12:49.720 --> 12:51.720
After all, it's your own career.

12:52.200 --> 12:54.660
I'm just helping you
weigh the pros and cons.

12:54.960 --> 12:56.840
The final decision is yours.

12:58.720 --> 13:01.510
I don't want to see my wife wronged,

13:02.360 --> 13:04.720
returning to school full of enthusiasm

13:05.150 --> 13:06.670
only to be shut out by them.

13:16.960 --> 13:18.760
Forget it. I won't say anything.

13:40.520 --> 13:49.650
[July 11, 2019, Thursday]

14:10.280 --> 14:14.990
[July 11, 2019, Thursday]

14:21.330 --> 14:24.730
[July 11, 2019, Thursday]

14:56.390 --> 14:56.960
You're right,

14:56.960 --> 14:57.440
Honey.

14:58.790 --> 14:59.550
If I go back,

15:01.000 --> 15:03.000
I might just be humiliating myself.

15:03.610 --> 15:05.810
You might not like what I'm about to say,

15:06.480 --> 15:07.540
but I have to say it.

15:09.010 --> 15:10.550
I can support you and Jiale.

15:12.060 --> 15:15.060
I don't want my wife
to suffer any injustice out there.

15:16.870 --> 15:17.440
Honey.

15:18.750 --> 15:21.720
I shouldn't have lost my temper with you.
I'm sorry.

15:26.910 --> 15:27.510
It's okay.

15:29.360 --> 15:30.390
I'm not mad at you.

15:32.550 --> 15:33.350
It's my fault.

15:34.270 --> 15:35.530
Please don't blame me.

15:37.200 --> 15:38.330
I'm not blaming you.

15:40.200 --> 15:41.130
Think about it.

15:42.200 --> 15:43.200
Think carefully.

15:45.090 --> 15:49.730
[International Medical Center]

15:50.360 --> 15:54.150
Patient No. 21, please go to Room 1.

15:55.080 --> 15:55.720
Hello.

15:56.910 --> 15:57.400
Hello.

15:58.080 --> 15:59.140
Please take a seat.

16:00.250 --> 16:00.910
Put it here.

16:04.030 --> 16:05.890
Where do you feel uncomfortable?

16:10.120 --> 16:11.320
I'm a police officer.

16:14.910 --> 16:15.580
Well,

16:16.870 --> 16:17.910
there's a case

16:18.910 --> 16:21.080
that's been quite troublesome recently.

16:21.080 --> 16:21.790
It's been

16:22.140 --> 16:23.810
keeping me awake all night,

16:23.870 --> 16:26.030
and I can't work properly during the day.

16:26.030 --> 16:28.270
I really don't know what to do,

16:28.270 --> 16:30.360
so I thought I'd come and see

16:30.550 --> 16:32.010
if I could get some relief.

16:32.910 --> 16:34.390
Since you're in this room,

16:34.390 --> 16:35.850
you're just a patient now.

16:35.870 --> 16:37.200
Whatever you say to me,

16:37.200 --> 16:38.850
I am obligated to keep it confidential.

16:38.850 --> 16:40.250
Well then. That's great.

16:40.630 --> 16:43.080
But will what you tell me

16:43.080 --> 16:43.910
include

16:43.910 --> 16:46.240
anything confidential from your system?

16:46.620 --> 16:48.220
That shouldn't be a problem.

16:49.000 --> 16:50.910
It's a case from many years ago.

16:51.630 --> 16:53.750
It must have been over a decade ago.

16:54.860 --> 16:55.860
Here's the thing.

16:58.120 --> 17:02.270
An ordinary, virtuous mother

17:03.670 --> 17:05.640
wanted to find a tutor for her son.

17:06.030 --> 17:06.920
Stop talking!

17:09.069 --> 17:10.270
I forgot everything.

17:10.480 --> 17:11.480
What if I told you

17:11.480 --> 17:13.880
that your mom left you
and your dad back then

17:14.300 --> 17:15.900
and later committed suicide

17:17.490 --> 17:19.750
because she was deceived by a bad person?

17:25.270 --> 17:26.670
He was a college student.

17:27.430 --> 17:28.430
He was quite nice.

17:29.200 --> 17:30.860
Other than tutoring me,

17:31.400 --> 17:32.430
he hardly spoke.

17:33.340 --> 17:35.140
Once, when my mom burned her hand

17:35.440 --> 17:36.350
while cooking,

17:37.110 --> 17:39.750
he even used a first-aid kit
to bandage it.

17:39.960 --> 17:41.290
My mom even praised him,

17:41.790 --> 17:44.190
saying that even though
he studied psychiatry,

17:44.190 --> 17:46.920
she didn't expect him
to be so skilled in surgery.

17:47.160 --> 17:48.760
But for some unknown reason,

17:49.350 --> 17:50.360
he got angry.

17:51.450 --> 17:54.580
He didn't come to our house for classes
for several days.

17:55.190 --> 17:56.220
I thought

17:57.530 --> 17:59.190
my mom would get me a new tutor.

18:00.270 --> 18:01.130
To my surprise,

18:01.830 --> 18:02.590
he came back.

18:04.480 --> 18:05.480
Since then,

18:06.270 --> 18:08.480
we became much closer.

18:10.070 --> 18:10.720
Later,

18:12.200 --> 18:14.730
he said he was going to study
in Harbor Island.

18:15.590 --> 18:18.520
My mom even secretly funded him
behind my dad's back.

18:21.200 --> 18:23.440
I've thought about it over and over again.

18:23.440 --> 18:23.990
If...

18:26.060 --> 18:28.660
If I had noticed something was wrong
back then,

18:30.200 --> 18:31.060
would my mom...

18:31.270 --> 18:32.790
not have left?

18:33.510 --> 18:35.310
It was two years later that the son

18:35.310 --> 18:36.910
heard from his mother again.

18:37.230 --> 18:38.960
He overheard his father's call

18:40.070 --> 18:41.600
and learned that his mother

18:41.920 --> 18:43.120
had taken her own life

18:43.880 --> 18:44.800
in Bingyuan.

18:50.310 --> 18:51.070
Don't drink!

18:54.750 --> 18:55.240
Don't.

18:59.480 --> 19:00.880
Do you know how she died?

19:17.250 --> 19:18.850
She was lying in the bathtub,

19:20.320 --> 19:21.320
covered in blood.

19:22.720 --> 19:23.780
She was all frozen,

19:25.520 --> 19:26.930
like an ice sculpture.

19:30.510 --> 19:33.310
The autopsy later revealed
that she was pregnant.

19:34.750 --> 19:35.880
Two lives were lost.

19:38.480 --> 19:39.340
And that son...

19:40.240 --> 19:42.790
His mother abandoned him

19:42.810 --> 19:43.940
for so-called love.

19:44.790 --> 19:46.200
His father was always away on business

19:46.200 --> 19:47.440
and had no time for him.

19:47.440 --> 19:49.440
He had to live with his grandmother.

19:49.510 --> 19:50.370
Not long after,

19:51.030 --> 19:53.230
his grandmother died of a broken heart.

19:53.860 --> 19:54.610
Well?

19:55.400 --> 19:56.830
A perfectly good family

19:57.920 --> 19:59.380
was ruined just like that.

20:01.110 --> 20:04.070
That bastard who deceived his Mom—

20:04.720 --> 20:06.880
shouldn't he be cut to pieces?

20:08.630 --> 20:09.630
That tutor—

20:12.920 --> 20:13.920
what was his name?

20:17.350 --> 20:18.010
Luo Liang.

20:34.070 --> 20:35.470
But from what I've heard,

20:37.190 --> 20:38.900
everything this mother did

20:39.900 --> 20:41.270
was her own choice.

20:42.830 --> 20:44.160
There was no deception.

20:45.200 --> 20:46.730
You sure know a lot about it.

20:48.400 --> 20:49.070
How could I?

20:49.680 --> 20:51.340
As a complete stranger,

20:51.590 --> 20:52.720
how could I know her?

20:52.720 --> 20:54.010
I'm just objectively

20:54.070 --> 20:55.330
analyzing your story.

20:56.660 --> 20:58.320
But what I'm curious about is—

20:58.940 --> 20:59.830
a case from ten years ago

20:59.830 --> 21:01.630
that was already ruled a suicide

21:02.030 --> 21:03.720
and didn't even happen in this city—

21:03.720 --> 21:06.050
why are you reopening the investigation?

21:10.640 --> 21:11.590
I mean,

21:13.020 --> 21:14.050
why is it

21:14.920 --> 21:16.140
bothering you?

21:19.480 --> 21:22.680
This actually involves
confidential case information.

21:23.160 --> 21:24.000
I can't say.

21:25.480 --> 21:26.580
All I can say is,

21:28.240 --> 21:29.070
I think

21:30.110 --> 21:31.910
her suicide was not that simple.

21:35.110 --> 21:36.110
What do you think?

21:51.640 --> 21:53.160
Actually, I don't know anything
about solving cases.

21:53.160 --> 21:54.820
I can't answer that question.

21:55.890 --> 21:57.090
Have a piece of candy.

21:57.640 --> 22:00.330
Having something sweet
can help relax your nerves.

22:00.330 --> 22:02.550
You police officers
are under too much stress.

22:02.550 --> 22:03.480
Right, right.

22:09.780 --> 22:11.440
Judging from your condition,

22:11.880 --> 22:13.270
you might have PTSD,

22:14.350 --> 22:16.280
post-traumatic stress disorder.

22:17.440 --> 22:19.240
It could be that the crime scenes

22:20.070 --> 22:21.800
had too much of an impact on you.

22:23.100 --> 22:25.230
It puts psychological pressure on you

22:25.240 --> 22:27.030
that you can't process right away.

22:27.030 --> 22:28.760
Actually, this is very normal.

22:28.790 --> 22:30.650
There's nothing to be ashamed of.

22:30.790 --> 22:32.790
And seeking help

22:32.790 --> 22:34.520
from a professional doctor now

22:34.640 --> 22:36.900
is something that should be encouraged.

22:37.590 --> 22:38.790
Thank you. Thank you.

22:39.680 --> 22:40.880
I'll prescribe some medicine for you.

22:40.880 --> 22:41.210
Okay.

22:42.240 --> 22:43.310
I'm glad I'm fine.

22:46.790 --> 22:47.920
Dr. Luo, according to

22:47.920 --> 22:49.270
the profile on the wall outside,

22:49.270 --> 22:51.440
you studied at a university in Chengyu?

22:51.440 --> 22:51.920
Yes.

22:53.130 --> 22:54.030
That's a coincidence.

22:54.030 --> 22:56.690
The family I just mentioned
was also in Chengyu.

22:57.440 --> 22:59.430
Wasn't their tutor studying medicine?

22:59.430 --> 23:01.210
Maybe you two met in school.

23:13.320 --> 23:14.520
Li Zhiheng?

23:14.680 --> 23:15.000
Yes.

23:18.410 --> 23:19.550
You are the police officer

23:19.550 --> 23:22.410
who was previously in charge of
Jian Leilei's case?

23:26.350 --> 23:26.830
Yes.

23:29.590 --> 23:30.880
I know Ms. Yan.

23:33.030 --> 23:33.470
Well...

23:33.470 --> 23:35.030
She mentioned to me before

23:35.030 --> 23:37.440
that you are a psychiatrist.

23:37.440 --> 23:39.240
That's why I came here.

23:39.240 --> 23:40.880
It's very hard
to make an appointment with you.

23:40.880 --> 23:42.550
I even paid extra
for a special consultation

23:42.550 --> 23:43.810
just to see you.

23:44.240 --> 23:46.040
You should have told me earlier.

23:46.400 --> 23:47.680
In this case,

23:47.680 --> 23:50.280
we have
multiple overlapping relationships.

23:50.880 --> 23:54.280
In principle, it would not be appropriate
for me to treat you.

23:54.900 --> 23:55.440
Is that so?

23:55.440 --> 23:56.750
Well...

23:56.750 --> 23:58.240
I really didn't know that.

23:58.640 --> 23:59.160
I just thought,

23:59.160 --> 24:00.720
since Ms. Yan

24:00.720 --> 24:03.240
is like my own sister,

24:03.240 --> 24:05.340
I should call you brother-in-law.

24:05.440 --> 24:07.880
I'll just say I'm feeling a bit unwell.

24:07.880 --> 24:09.090
Coming to see my brother-in-law
for a checkup

24:09.090 --> 24:10.290
is perfectly normal.

24:11.030 --> 24:12.890
So don't worry, brother-in-law.

24:13.240 --> 24:15.170
Ms. Yan's business is my business.

24:15.590 --> 24:16.120
No matter

24:16.440 --> 24:18.200
what happens to my sister,

24:18.480 --> 24:19.640
as her brother,

24:20.400 --> 24:21.600
I will take care of it.

24:25.270 --> 24:27.530
Then I must thank you on her behalf first.

24:27.960 --> 24:28.890
But regardless,

24:29.440 --> 24:31.100
it's best if nothing happens,

24:31.400 --> 24:31.960
right?

24:32.880 --> 24:33.560
Of course.

24:35.750 --> 24:38.550
I've prescribed
some nerve-relaxing pills for you.

24:38.550 --> 24:40.480
Take one when you can't sleep well.

24:41.090 --> 24:42.680
It has a calming effect
and helps you focus.

24:42.680 --> 24:43.510
Okay.

24:51.830 --> 24:54.160
I got this when I was a kid,
playing around,

24:54.310 --> 24:56.440
and burned myself on a kerosene stove.

24:58.440 --> 24:59.840
It looks pretty serious.

25:00.680 --> 25:02.770
Alright, I won't bother you anymore.

25:04.160 --> 25:06.000
Well, we should

25:06.000 --> 25:06.640
have a meal together

25:06.640 --> 25:07.920
with Ms. Yan sometime.

25:08.070 --> 25:08.590
No problem.

25:08.590 --> 25:09.750
Let's meet formally.

25:09.750 --> 25:10.080
Okay.

25:10.720 --> 25:10.960
Alright.

25:10.960 --> 25:12.000
I'll let you get back to work.

25:12.000 --> 25:12.370
Okay.

25:13.750 --> 25:15.070
You should drink less iced drinks.

25:15.070 --> 25:16.530
It's bad for your stomach.

25:42.640 --> 25:43.700
Hello, Dr. Luo.

25:43.960 --> 25:44.440
Hello.

27:16.150 --> 27:21.590
[Department Dean's Office]

27:24.880 --> 27:26.140
-Mrs. Feng?
-Yan Ling?

27:27.750 --> 27:29.440
You're looking for Director Lin, right?

27:29.440 --> 27:31.440
He's talking with a student inside.

27:32.960 --> 27:34.790
It's fine. I'll wait.

27:35.650 --> 27:36.650
Th-That's fine.

27:36.680 --> 27:37.830
Please wait a moment.

27:37.830 --> 27:40.630
I need to sign a form
at the Student Affairs Office.

27:41.270 --> 27:42.670
I won't keep you company.

27:42.790 --> 27:43.790
Go ahead, please.

27:49.780 --> 27:54.130
[Guo Loulou Street] [Zeze Road]

28:15.240 --> 28:17.410
I want to trim it a bit more.

28:17.960 --> 28:19.180
It'll look nicer if they are crossed.

28:19.180 --> 28:20.160
Crossed?

28:20.160 --> 28:20.650
Not bad.

28:20.800 --> 28:21.900
What about this one?

28:21.900 --> 28:22.500
Stop.

28:23.240 --> 28:24.160
Jiale?

28:24.550 --> 28:25.030
Mom?

28:25.480 --> 28:26.520
Why are you here?

28:28.350 --> 28:29.960
Dr. Luo brought me here.

28:30.800 --> 28:32.730
And we bought flowers for Grandma.

28:32.740 --> 28:35.340
They're the lilies
she and Grandpa liked best.

28:36.150 --> 28:37.880
That's very thoughtful of you.

28:39.190 --> 28:40.590
I didn't even think of it.

28:41.590 --> 28:43.250
We just bought them on the way.

28:43.510 --> 28:46.350
Why are you holding your stomach?
Are you not feeling well?

28:46.350 --> 28:47.750
My stomach is a bit upset.

28:47.750 --> 28:49.430
It's fine.
I'll be okay after resting for a while.

28:49.430 --> 28:50.680
Then go inside and rest.

28:50.680 --> 28:51.140
No need.

28:51.540 --> 28:53.270
Go ahead. I'll take care of him.

28:56.120 --> 28:58.180
Here, Jiale. I'm leaving this to you.

28:59.940 --> 29:00.700
Jiale.

29:02.030 --> 29:03.350
What do you want to eat for dinner?

29:03.350 --> 29:04.880
I will cook it for you, okay?

29:05.880 --> 29:07.210
Anything would be fine.

29:07.500 --> 29:09.500
Cola chicken wings? How about that?

29:10.480 --> 29:10.880
Okay.

29:11.030 --> 29:11.520
Okay.

29:11.680 --> 29:13.280
Let's make it together then.

29:14.270 --> 29:15.130
Go to your room.

29:15.520 --> 29:17.200
-I'll take a nap then.
-Go.

29:22.040 --> 29:22.960
This one hasn't been trimmed yet.

29:22.960 --> 29:23.690
This one has.

29:25.390 --> 29:25.920
Jiale.

29:27.680 --> 29:29.330
A lot of things happened to Mom recently,

29:29.330 --> 29:30.680
and she's not in a good mood.

29:30.680 --> 29:31.550
That's why she forgot

29:31.550 --> 29:33.080
to buy flowers for Grandma.

29:36.400 --> 29:39.380
We were just talking about
Grandpa and Grandma.

29:39.720 --> 29:41.030
Don't ask her about it,

29:41.630 --> 29:43.490
so she won't get sad again.

29:47.740 --> 29:49.430
I miss Grandma a little.

29:51.830 --> 29:55.030
Although she was
very strict with me before,

29:56.070 --> 29:59.200
she was really, really good to me
before she passed away.

29:59.680 --> 30:00.830
If only Mom had apologized

30:00.830 --> 30:02.480
to Grandma earlier.

30:03.030 --> 30:05.490
We could have been
together happily sooner.

30:11.160 --> 30:12.720
Mom is quite stubborn.

30:13.400 --> 30:15.030
We need to be more understanding of her.

30:15.030 --> 30:16.070
We're boys,

30:17.160 --> 30:19.510
so we should be more considerate, okay?

30:21.070 --> 30:23.680
Come on, put the new flowers in quickly.

30:24.540 --> 30:25.600
Then we'll go cook.

30:25.750 --> 30:26.110
Okay?

30:35.640 --> 30:36.480
Chicken wings.

30:36.480 --> 30:37.540
Careful, it's hot.

30:37.640 --> 30:38.110
Jiale,

30:38.110 --> 30:38.640
look.

30:38.920 --> 30:40.030
How's the shrimp I cooked?

30:40.030 --> 30:40.480
Good.

30:40.630 --> 30:41.200
Let's plate it.

30:41.200 --> 30:42.130
Five Blessings.

30:43.310 --> 30:44.710
I'll add some garnish.

30:44.980 --> 30:46.320
Okay, garnish it.

30:52.920 --> 30:53.500
Jiale.

30:53.920 --> 30:55.160
This is called parsley.

30:55.160 --> 30:57.090
Help me sprinkle some later, okay?

30:59.160 --> 30:59.550
Here.

31:01.590 --> 31:02.760
Chef.

31:10.880 --> 31:11.920
I'm sorry.

31:12.400 --> 31:14.000
I just wanted to take a short nap.

31:14.000 --> 31:15.600
I didn't expect to sleep so long.

31:15.600 --> 31:17.240
It's fine. You're up just in time.

31:17.240 --> 31:18.200
I was afraid you'd sleep too long

31:18.200 --> 31:19.730
and the food would get cold.

31:20.070 --> 31:21.930
Is there anything I can help with?

31:22.000 --> 31:22.640
It's fine.

31:22.880 --> 31:24.160
Your cooking is just so-so anyway.

31:24.160 --> 31:25.790
Look at what Dr. Luo and I made.

31:25.790 --> 31:27.720
It can rival Godmother's cooking.

31:32.400 --> 31:34.380
Looks like I really need to learn.

31:34.550 --> 31:36.400
No need, just stay there

31:36.400 --> 31:37.680
and let us serve you.

31:37.790 --> 31:38.310
Yeah.

31:38.590 --> 31:40.550
Before, it was Godmother and Grandma
serving you.

31:40.550 --> 31:41.720
Now it's our turn.

31:48.680 --> 31:49.510
Yan Jiale,

31:50.000 --> 31:52.130
you're being ungrateful saying that.

31:52.680 --> 31:54.830
Who usually folds your clothes

31:54.880 --> 31:56.140
and washes your shoes?

31:56.200 --> 31:57.730
Grandma used to do them too.

32:02.270 --> 32:03.110
Jiale,

32:03.440 --> 32:04.720
be considerate.

32:05.200 --> 32:06.550
Cola is probably hungry too.

32:06.550 --> 32:07.410
Help me feed it.

32:07.790 --> 32:08.240
Okay.

32:09.070 --> 32:09.400
Wait,

32:09.400 --> 32:09.960
Mom.

32:13.400 --> 32:15.400
Wipe off any unboiled water from it.

32:15.510 --> 32:18.370
Cola will get diarrhea
if it drinks unboiled water.

32:19.960 --> 32:20.790
Got it.

32:22.070 --> 32:24.200
You don't even care about me that much.

32:24.310 --> 32:25.510
You're not a hamster.

32:26.550 --> 32:27.810
Jiale, serve the food.

32:28.430 --> 32:29.550
What are we missing?

32:29.550 --> 32:30.750
Let's make some okra.

32:30.770 --> 32:31.240
Okay.

32:31.960 --> 32:32.960
You add the sauce.

32:33.750 --> 32:34.680
Just like a chef,

32:34.680 --> 32:36.140
sprinkle it on with flair.

32:42.180 --> 32:43.340
Like a lion.

32:43.590 --> 32:44.070
Lion.

32:44.510 --> 32:45.840
Show your canine teeth.

32:48.480 --> 32:49.880
The left side.

32:50.920 --> 32:51.440
Left.

32:51.960 --> 32:53.070
Right side.

32:54.790 --> 32:56.000
Okay, all clean.

32:56.110 --> 32:56.720
Spit.

32:58.750 --> 33:00.210
Come on, let's go to sleep.

33:01.550 --> 33:02.670
Good night, Mom.

33:02.790 --> 33:03.450
Good night.

33:04.270 --> 33:04.960
Fly!

33:07.680 --> 33:09.610
Come, get under the covers, Jiale.

33:12.270 --> 33:12.930
Go to sleep.

33:24.250 --> 33:26.280
You should have told me in advance.

33:26.920 --> 33:27.960
Jiale is back,

33:28.120 --> 33:29.850
but I didn't even get prepared.

33:34.160 --> 33:35.220
Are you blaming me?

33:36.480 --> 33:37.000
No.

33:38.400 --> 33:40.160
I wanted to give you a surprise.

33:41.200 --> 33:42.600
I thought you'd be happy.

33:43.310 --> 33:44.710
I'm Jiale's stepfather.

33:45.350 --> 33:46.480
And he likes me.

33:47.310 --> 33:49.590
I thought you'd be happy to see all this,

33:50.550 --> 33:51.200
but I didn't expect that

33:51.200 --> 33:52.720
your concern would be

33:53.070 --> 33:55.530
that I brought him back
without telling you.

33:56.480 --> 33:57.310
Of course I'm happy

33:57.310 --> 33:58.790
that you brought him back.

34:01.200 --> 34:02.550
Why are you angry?

34:03.750 --> 34:04.400
No.

34:05.590 --> 34:07.920
Your tone just now was very strange.

34:09.110 --> 34:10.310
Even if it weren't me,

34:10.550 --> 34:12.070
just an ordinary friend—

34:12.480 --> 34:14.610
like the mother of Jiale's classmate—

34:14.880 --> 34:16.400
if she brought Jiale home,

34:16.550 --> 34:18.670
would you question her first,

34:19.000 --> 34:20.360
asking why she did it,

34:20.760 --> 34:22.400
instead of thanking her?

34:22.670 --> 34:24.550
How could I be questioning you?

34:25.190 --> 34:27.710
I'm very grateful
that you brought Jiale back

34:27.710 --> 34:29.370
and bought flowers for my mom.

34:30.110 --> 34:31.110
What I mean is,

34:31.110 --> 34:32.880
in the future,
if you make arrangements like this,

34:32.880 --> 34:34.800
could you let me know in advance

34:35.070 --> 34:36.400
so I can be prepared?

34:38.190 --> 34:38.670
Okay.

34:39.550 --> 34:40.230
I got it.

34:40.960 --> 34:41.820
It's my fault.

34:42.190 --> 34:44.000
From now on, every message Jiale sends me,

34:44.000 --> 34:44.960
every call he makes,

34:44.960 --> 34:46.690
I'll report to you completely.

34:46.760 --> 34:48.190
If he ever asks me to pick him up,

34:48.190 --> 34:49.590
I'll make sure I have

34:49.590 --> 34:50.280
your permission first.

34:50.280 --> 34:51.070
Is that okay?

34:51.360 --> 34:52.880
I didn't mean that.

34:53.920 --> 34:55.850
Why are you being so unreasonable?

34:56.659 --> 34:58.440
Me? I'm being unreasonable?

34:58.590 --> 35:00.280
Now it's me who's being unreasonable?

35:00.280 --> 35:01.900
I know you've been in a bad mood lately,

35:01.900 --> 35:03.510
and you're not feeling well today.

35:03.510 --> 35:05.760
I picked Jiale up, cooked, and cleaned up,

35:05.760 --> 35:07.360
and I'm being unreasonable?

35:09.330 --> 35:10.400
Jiale and I guessed that

35:10.400 --> 35:12.510
you'd be super happy
to see him when you got back.

35:12.510 --> 35:14.000
You weren't as happy as we imagined,

35:14.000 --> 35:14.800
which is fine,

35:14.970 --> 35:16.080
but you had absolutely no reaction

35:16.080 --> 35:17.240
to our efforts.

35:17.550 --> 35:19.330
It's okay if you wrong me,

35:19.400 --> 35:20.940
but it's not fair to Jiale.

35:21.320 --> 35:22.920
How could I have no reaction?

35:24.320 --> 35:25.920
I know you've done a lot.

35:26.070 --> 35:27.190
-I'm so gr-
-Forget it.

35:27.190 --> 35:28.110
Let's leave it at that.

35:28.110 --> 35:30.960
We've been arguing for so long
over such a small thing.

35:30.960 --> 35:31.590
I'll go wash up outside.

35:31.590 --> 35:33.160
I didn't blame you.

35:33.190 --> 35:33.550
I...

35:47.150 --> 35:47.960
Honey.

35:50.000 --> 35:51.580
Honey, don't be angry.

35:51.760 --> 35:53.080
Listen to me.

35:53.280 --> 35:54.760
I didn't blame you.

35:55.070 --> 35:56.440
You misunderstood me.

36:22.920 --> 36:23.980
Have some hot milk.

36:24.280 --> 36:25.740
It helps you sleep better.

36:32.110 --> 36:35.000
Honey, I really didn't blame you just now,

36:35.800 --> 36:37.730
but you suddenly lost your temper.

36:38.480 --> 36:40.610
I don't even know how to talk to you now.

36:42.800 --> 36:44.360
Alright, alright.

36:44.510 --> 36:45.230
I know.

36:46.400 --> 36:47.590
My bad, okay?

36:49.890 --> 36:51.170
I'm not mad at you.

36:52.110 --> 36:53.240
You're in a bad mood.

36:53.480 --> 36:54.510
Did you go to the school again

36:54.510 --> 36:55.770
and something happen?

36:59.880 --> 37:02.070
I waited outside Director Lin's office

37:02.070 --> 37:03.110
for a long time,

37:04.070 --> 37:05.730
but in the end, I didn't get in.

37:09.590 --> 37:10.230
Why?

37:11.880 --> 37:13.760
I saw Mrs. Feng at the door.

37:15.110 --> 37:17.040
I feel like she's been avoiding me.

37:18.710 --> 37:20.280
And the way she looked at me

37:20.920 --> 37:23.760
was as if she believed
I was that kind of person.

37:25.480 --> 37:26.680
I didn't want to go in.

37:27.280 --> 37:29.080
I didn't know what to say to them.

37:33.280 --> 37:36.080
You don't need to beg
for their forgiveness at all.

37:37.190 --> 37:39.190
Since they make you uncomfortable,

37:39.330 --> 37:40.400
we shouldn't give them

37:40.400 --> 37:42.200
the right to give you a hard time.

37:42.530 --> 37:44.590
We'll mind our own business from now on.

37:44.590 --> 37:45.800
Why do you have to

37:45.800 --> 37:46.480
beg them so pathetically,

37:46.480 --> 37:47.510
letting them pity

37:48.150 --> 37:49.080
and laugh at you?

37:52.760 --> 37:54.090
After I left the school,

37:55.400 --> 37:57.400
I sat alone in the car for a long time.

37:58.400 --> 38:00.530
I can say with a clear conscience that,

38:00.710 --> 38:01.670
as a teacher,

38:02.670 --> 38:04.670
my academic level is up to standard,

38:05.760 --> 38:07.590
and I am conscientious and responsible

38:07.590 --> 38:08.720
toward my students.

38:11.000 --> 38:12.150
Although morally,

38:13.230 --> 38:14.160
I have a blemish,

38:16.000 --> 38:17.280
isn't Ding Zhibo

38:17.280 --> 38:18.590
the real culprit?

38:20.070 --> 38:21.530
If I just resign like this,

38:22.320 --> 38:24.590
won't it show
that I have a guilty conscience

38:24.590 --> 38:26.390
and confirm their opinion of me?

38:28.320 --> 38:28.920
Honey,

38:30.510 --> 38:31.510
I don't want this.

38:32.510 --> 38:34.440
I don't want to back down like this.

38:40.000 --> 38:40.590
Okay.

38:41.670 --> 38:44.000
I'll support whatever decision you make.

38:44.320 --> 38:46.000
Don't think about anything now.

38:46.000 --> 38:47.000
Go to sleep first.

38:47.320 --> 38:48.590
We'll talk tomorrow.

38:52.960 --> 38:53.590
Honey,

38:54.400 --> 38:55.670
don't be angry.

38:56.920 --> 38:59.520
I know everything
you've done for me and Jiale.

39:00.550 --> 39:01.960
I'm very grateful to you.

39:04.960 --> 39:05.760
It's fine.

39:06.590 --> 39:07.590
I'm not angry.

39:08.880 --> 39:09.360
Really.

39:11.360 --> 39:12.190
I'm not angry.

39:36.360 --> 39:37.070
Yuan.

39:37.630 --> 39:39.560
Mom will make you a bowl of wontons.

39:42.040 --> 39:42.920
What's wrong?

39:43.320 --> 39:43.920
Yuan?

39:45.150 --> 39:45.950
What's wrong?

39:51.510 --> 39:52.510
Yuan!

39:53.230 --> 39:54.150
Yuan!

39:56.830 --> 40:00.400
[Son]

40:02.930 --> 40:07.250
[Son]

40:07.310 --> 40:09.700
[Wuzhou People's Hospital]

40:12.680 --> 40:14.110
[Emergency Room]

40:18.610 --> 40:20.460
[Emergency Room]

40:19.920 --> 40:21.840
Who are Xiao Yuan's family members?

40:21.840 --> 40:31.170
[Chinese Pharmacy] [Western Pharmacy]
[Emergency Ultrasound Room] [Injection Room]

40:21.930 --> 40:22.440
I am.

40:22.550 --> 40:23.170
I am.

40:23.760 --> 40:25.400
How is my daughter?

40:26.710 --> 40:28.620
She's temporarily out of danger.

40:29.070 --> 40:30.110
If you had come 10 minutes later,

40:30.110 --> 40:32.240
we might not have been able to save her.

40:33.760 --> 40:34.230
Well...

40:35.150 --> 40:36.880
what exactly is wrong with her?

40:37.670 --> 40:39.440
You don't know?

40:39.550 --> 40:40.880
She has drug poisoning.

40:40.960 --> 40:41.440
Drug?

40:41.920 --> 40:42.630
Poisoning?

40:45.110 --> 40:47.170
What medicine does she usually take?

40:49.840 --> 40:55.250
[Emergency Room]

40:50.110 --> 40:52.110
She has a mental illness.

40:52.800 --> 40:54.930
The medicine she takes is all for this.

40:55.760 --> 40:56.840
I can't read.

40:57.400 --> 40:59.800
I can only give her the pills
by their color.

41:00.070 --> 41:02.800
Then which hospital did you take her to?

41:02.880 --> 41:05.480
Which doctor prescribed
the medicine for her?

41:06.550 --> 41:08.800
A doctor from out of town.

41:09.150 --> 41:09.960
A...

41:10.110 --> 41:11.960
A doctor from our hometown.

41:13.960 --> 41:16.480
What about the burns on her body?

41:17.360 --> 41:17.880
Well...

41:18.550 --> 41:19.840
I don't know.

41:20.360 --> 41:21.510
She went out to work

41:21.880 --> 41:23.550
and came back like this.

41:24.320 --> 41:26.030
And her mind was also damaged.

41:27.190 --> 41:27.840
I see.

41:28.400 --> 41:29.800
Wait here first.

41:29.800 --> 41:30.800
I'll go get you a form.

41:30.800 --> 41:32.460
She needs to be hospitalized.

41:32.550 --> 41:33.840
Don't move. Just wait.

41:34.800 --> 41:35.280
Okay.

41:41.190 --> 41:42.070
Call the police immediately.

41:42.070 --> 41:44.470
There's something wrong with this mother.

41:48.470 --> 41:54.930
[July 12, 2019, Friday]
[Case Filing Chamber]

41:48.880 --> 41:50.030
Think harder.

41:50.590 --> 41:52.520
See if there are any other details.

42:04.070 --> 42:05.130
I'll ask you again.

42:05.800 --> 42:06.840
What's

42:07.510 --> 42:09.400
your relationship with this girl?

42:09.400 --> 42:10.540
She's my daughter.

42:11.670 --> 42:12.280
Ma'am,

42:13.070 --> 42:14.190
you have type O blood,

42:14.190 --> 42:15.590
and she has type AB blood.

42:15.920 --> 42:17.450
Do you know what that means?

42:18.340 --> 42:19.080
No.

42:19.760 --> 42:20.670
It means

42:21.000 --> 42:23.000
she couldn't possibly be your daughter.

42:23.000 --> 42:24.070
Who exactly is she?

42:25.070 --> 42:25.470
She...

42:25.960 --> 42:27.440
is my daughter.

42:31.880 --> 42:33.400
Then where did these pills you gave her

42:33.400 --> 42:34.440
come from?

42:34.920 --> 42:36.850
These are all prescription drugs.

42:36.880 --> 42:38.480
Without a doctor's prescription,

42:38.480 --> 42:40.740
you can't buy them at a regular pharmacy.

42:41.440 --> 42:43.570
Which doctor prescribed them for her?

42:44.270 --> 42:48.970
[The Dark Romance]

42:51.440 --> 42:52.580
I've turned it off!

42:52.750 --> 42:53.800
The fire is gone now.

42:53.800 --> 42:54.480
Fire, fire!

42:54.710 --> 42:55.880
The fire is gone now! It's gone!

42:55.880 --> 42:57.280
Stand up!

42:57.590 --> 42:58.220
Mom!

42:58.480 --> 42:59.140
Mom's here.

42:59.650 --> 43:00.310
Mom's here.

43:00.390 --> 43:01.300
After I leave,

43:02.590 --> 43:04.420
remember to give her the medicine.

43:04.420 --> 43:06.550
I've already put it in the nightstand.

43:06.840 --> 43:08.170
Don't miss a single day.

43:08.840 --> 43:12.070
The small ones,
2 times a day, 3 pills each time.

43:12.590 --> 43:15.000
The big ones, 3 times a day,

43:15.000 --> 43:15.890
4 pills each time.

43:15.890 --> 43:17.450
What illness does she have

43:18.070 --> 43:19.800
that she needs to take so much medicine?

43:19.800 --> 43:20.800
You don't need to ask.

43:20.800 --> 43:22.330
Just give her the medicine.

43:24.050 --> 43:26.490
I have a bad memory and can't remember it.

43:26.550 --> 43:27.800
I'll write it down.

43:27.800 --> 43:29.030
Don't write it down.

43:29.030 --> 43:31.330
Just keep it in your mind.

43:31.550 --> 43:33.670
Not a day missed, and not a pill less.

43:35.520 --> 43:36.730
Take good care of her.

43:37.620 --> 43:38.910
I'll pack up and go back.
